<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>Posts</h1>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Title</th>
      <th>Content</th>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @posts.each do |post| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= post.title %></td>
        <td><%= post.content %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Show', post_path(post_id: post.id), method: :get %></td> <%#post는 post_path(id:post.id) 또는 post_path(post)와 같음, 따로 method를 안써주면 기본 메소드는 get%>
       <%#<td><%= link_to 'Show',post % ></td>  축약형 %>
        <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_post_path(post) %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', post, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>

<br>

<%= link_to 'New Post', new_post_path %>
